  "content": "<div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\">\n\n            <header class=\"mb-12 text-center dark:text-center\">\n              <div class=\"inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-[#E0EFC7] dark:bg-[#E0EFC7]/20 rounded-full text-[#FF3131] dark:text-[#FF6B6B] font-medium text-sm mb-4\">\n                {t.blog.multiCat.category}\n              </div>\n              <h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50\">\n                {t.blog.multiCat.title}\n              </h1>\n              <p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto\">\n                {t.blog.multiCat.description}\n              </p>\n              <div class=\"flex items-center justify-center space-x-4 mt-6 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400\">\n                <span>{t.blog.multiCat.publishDate}</span>\n                <span>‚Ä¢</span>\n                <span>{t.blog.multiCat.readTime}</span>\n              </div>\n            </header>\n\n            <div class=\"mb-12\">\n              <img src=\"heroImage\" alt=\"Multiple cats in a household demonstrating the need for effective multi-cat litter deodorizing solutions\" />\n              <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-center mt-2\">\n                Multi-cat households face unique odor challenges requiring specialized deodorizing solutions\n              </p>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-800 rounded-lg p-6 mb-12\">\n              <h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-100 mb-4\">üê± {t.blog.multiCat.stats.title}</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-200\">\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\n                  <div class=\"text-2xl font-bold\">3.2x</div>\n                  <div class=\"text-sm\">{t.blog.multiCat.stats.strongerOdors}</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\n                  <div class=\"text-2xl font-bold\">1+1</div>\n                  <div class=\"text-sm\">{t.blog.multiCat.stats.litterBoxes}</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\n                  <div class=\"text-2xl font-bold\">2-3x</div>\n                  <div class=\"text-sm\">{t.blog.multiCat.stats.moreDeodorizer}</div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"text-center\">\n                  <div class=\"text-2xl font-bold\">Daily</div>\n                  <div class=\"text-sm\">{t.blog.multiCat.stats.maintenance}</div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\">\n              <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mb-6\">Why Multi-Cat Households Face Unique Odor Challenges</h2>\n\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-6\">\n                If you're searching for the <strong>best litter deodorizer for multi-cat</strong> households,\n                you're facing challenges that single-cat owners simply don't understand. Multiple cats create\n                exponentially stronger odors, not just additive ones.\n              </p>\n\n              <div class=\"bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/20 border-l-4 border-yellow-400 dark:border-yellow-700 p-6 mb-8\">\n                <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-yellow-900 dark:text-yellow-100 mb-3\">üî¨ The Science Behind Multi-Cat Odors</h3>\n                <ul class=\"text-yellow-800 dark:text-yellow-200 space-y-2\">\n                  <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Ammonia Concentration:</strong> 2+ cats create 4x stronger ammonia levels</li>\n                  <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Bacterial Growth:</strong> Warm, moist environment accelerates decomposition</li>\n                  <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Territory Marking:</strong> Stress-induced stronger urine scents</li>\n                  <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Box Traffic:</strong> Constant use prevents proper drying between uses</li>\n                  <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Compound Effects:</strong> Different cats' waste chemistry interacts</li>\n                </ul>\n              </div>\n\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-8\">\n                This isn't just about having more cats - it's about managing a complex ecosystem\n                where traditional single-cat solutions simply fail. You need <strong>multi-cat litter deodorizer</strong>\n                strategies designed for these intensified conditions.\n              </p>\n\n              <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mb-6\">The #1 Solution: Activated Carbon Technology</h2>\n\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-6\">\n                After testing dozens of products in real multi-cat environments, activated carbon\n                consistently outperforms all alternatives. Here's why it's the gold standard for\n                <strong>odor control multi-cat</strong> households:\n              </p>\n\n              <div class=\"bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 border border-green-200 dark:border-green-800 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8\">\n                <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-green-900 dark:text-green-100 mb-4\">‚ö° Why Activated Carbon Wins</h3>\n                <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-green-800 dark:text-green-200\">\n                  <div>\n                    <h4 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">üéØ Superior Absorption</h4>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm\">Absorbs 1000x more odor molecules than baking soda per gram</p>\n                  </div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h4 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">üîÑ Continuous Action</h4>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm\">Works 24/7 without losing effectiveness over time</p>\n                  </div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h4 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">üö´ No Masking</h4>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm\">Actually eliminates odors instead of covering them up</p>\n                  </div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h4 class=\"font-bold mb-2\">üê± Fragrance-Free Formula</h4>\n                    <p class=\"text-sm\">No added fragrances or dyes; commonly used in household filtration</p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mb-6\">Multi-Cat Dosage Calculator</h2>\n\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-6\">\n                Getting the dosage right is critical for multi-cat success. Too little won't control\n                the intensified odors; too much wastes product and can create dust.\n              </p>\n\n              <div class=\"bg-[#FF3131]/10 dark:bg-[#FF3131]/5 border border-[#FF3131]/20 dark:border-[#FF6B6B]/30 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8\">\n                <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-[#FF3131] dark:text-[#FF6B6B] mb-4\">üìä Exact Dosage Formula</h3>\n                <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n                  <div class=\"bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600\">\n                    <div class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mb-2\">Base Formula:</div>\n                    <div class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200\">1 teaspoon per cat per litter box</div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4\">\n                    <div class=\"bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 p-4 rounded-lg\">\n                      <div class=\"font-bold text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-100\">2 Cats, 3 Boxes</div>\n                      <div class=\"text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-200 text-sm\">3 tsp daily = 120g lasts 5-6 weeks</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-900/20 p-4 rounded-lg\">\n                      <div class=\"font-bold text-purple-900 dark:text-purple-100\">3 Cats, 4 Boxes</div>\n                      <div class=\"text-purple-800 dark:text-purple-200 text-sm\">4 tsp daily = 120g lasts 4-5 weeks</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-900/20 p-4 rounded-lg\">\n                      <div class=\"font-bold text-orange-900 dark:text-orange-100\">4+ Cats</div>\n                      <div class=\"text-orange-800 dark:text-orange-200 text-sm\">120g size provides best value for large households</div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <div class=\"mb-8\">\n                <img src=\"multiBoxImage\" alt=\"Strategic litter box setup for multi-cat household odor management\" />\n                <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-center mt-2\">\n                  Strategic litter box placement is crucial for multi-cat households\n                </p>\n              </div>\n\n              <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mb-6\">Multi-Cat Litter Box Strategy</h2>\n\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-6\">\n                The <strong>activated carbon multi-cat litter</strong> approach requires strategic box\n                placement and management. Here's the proven system used by professional catteries:\n              </p>\n\n              <div class=\"space-y-8 mb-12\">\n                \n                <div class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg p-6\">\n                  <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mb-4\">üìç Strategic Box Placement</h3>\n                  <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                    <div>\n                      <h4 class=\"font-bold text-green-700 dark:text-green-300 mb-3\">‚úÖ High-Traffic Zones</h4>\n                      <ul class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 space-y-2\">\n                        <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Main bathroom:</strong> Best ventilation + easy cleaning</li>\n                        <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Laundry room:</strong> Away from food areas</li>\n                        <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Basement:</strong> Natural odor containment</li>\n                      </ul>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <h4 class=\"font-bold text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300 mb-3\">üéØ Secondary Locations</h4>\n                      <ul class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 space-y-2\">\n                        <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Spare bathroom:</strong> Reduces territorial disputes</li>\n                        <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Large closet:</strong> With ventilation fan</li>\n                        <li>‚Ä¢ <strong>Covered porch:</strong> Maximum fresh air circulation</li>\n                      </ul>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                  <div class=\"mt-4 p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg\">\n                    <strong class=\"text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50\">Pro Tip:</strong>\n                    <span class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200\"> Space boxes at least 3 feet apart to prevent territorial issues while maintaining easy access for daily maintenance.</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg p-6\">\n                  <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mb-4\">‚è∞ Multi-Cat Maintenance Schedule</h3>\n                  <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4\">\n                    <div class=\"bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 p-4 rounded-lg\">\n                      <h4 class=\"font-bold text-red-900 dark:text-red-100 mb-2\">üåÖ Morning (5 minutes)</h4>\n                      <ul class=\"text-red-800 dark:text-red-200 text-sm space-y-1\">\n                        <li>‚Ä¢ Quick scoop high-traffic boxes</li>\n                        <li>‚Ä¢ Add fresh deodorizer to used boxes</li>\n                        <li>‚Ä¢ Visual odor check</li>\n                      </ul>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 p-4 rounded-lg\">\n                      <h4 class=\"font-bold text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-100 mb-2\">üåÜ Evening (10 minutes)</h4>\n                      <ul class=\"text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-200 text-sm space-y-1\">\n                        <li>‚Ä¢ Complete scoop of all boxes</li>\n                        <li>‚Ä¢ Level and redistribute litter</li>\n                        <li>‚Ä¢ Apply deodorizer to any problem areas</li>\n                      </ul>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20 p-4 rounded-lg\">\n                      <h4 class=\"font-bold text-green-900 dark:text-green-100 mb-2\">üìÖ Weekly (45 minutes)</h4>\n                      <ul class=\"text-green-800 dark:text-green-200 text-sm space-y-1\">\n                        <li>‚Ä¢ Complete litter replacement</li>\n                        <li>‚Ä¢ Box deep cleaning with enzyme cleaner</li>\n                        <li>‚Ä¢ Fresh deodorizer base layer</li>\n                      </ul>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg p-6\">\n                  <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mb-4\">‚ùå Avoid These Multi-Cat Mistakes</h3>\n                  <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start space-x-3\">\n                      <span class=\"text-red-500 dark:text-red-400 text-xl\">üö´</span>\n                      <div>\n                        <strong class=\"text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50\">Using Single-Cat Amounts:</strong>\n                        <span class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200\"> Multi-cat homes need 2-3x more deodorizer than single-cat calculations suggest.</span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start space-x-3\">\n                      <span class=\"text-red-500 dark:text-red-400 text-xl\">üö´</span>\n                      <div>\n                        <strong class=\"text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50\">Mixing Different Deodorizers:</strong>\n                        <span class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200\"> Chemical interactions can reduce effectiveness or create unwanted odors.</span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start space-x-3\">\n                      <span class=\"text-red-500 dark:text-red-400 text-xl\">üö´</span>\n                      <div>\n                        <strong class=\"text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50\">Relying on Scented Products:</strong>\n                        <span class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200\"> Fragrances overwhelm cats' sensitive noses and can cause litter box avoidance.</span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start space-x-3\">\n                      <span class=\"text-red-500 dark:text-red-400 text-xl\">üö´</span>\n                      <div>\n                        <strong class=\"text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50\">Inconsistent Application:</strong>\n                        <span class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200\"> Skipping days allows odors to compound and become much harder to eliminate.</span>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mb-6\">Comparison: Multi-Cat Deodorizer Options</h2>\n\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-6\">\n                Not all <strong>cat litter additive multiple cats</strong> products are created equal.\n                Here's how the most popular options perform in real multi-cat environments:\n              </p>\n\n              <div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-8\">\n                <table class=\"w-full border-collapse border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-lg\">\n                  <thead>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800\">\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 p-3 text-left text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 font-bold\">Product Type</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 p-3 text-left text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 font-bold\">Multi-Cat Effectiveness</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 p-3 text-left text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 font-bold\">Duration</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 p-3 text-left text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 font-bold\">Monthly Cost</th>\n                    </tr>\n                  </thead>\n                  <tbody>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/20\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 p-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200\">\n                        <strong>Activated Carbon (Purrify)</strong>\n                      </td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 p-3 text-green-700 dark:text-green-300\">\n                        <strong>Excellent</strong> - Handles 4+ cats\n                      </td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 p-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200\">\n                        5-7 days per application\n                      </td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 p-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200\">\n                        $25-35 (3-4 cats)\n                      </td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 p-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200\">\n                        <strong>Baking Soda</strong>\n                      </td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 p-3 text-yellow-700 dark:text-yellow-300\">\n                        <strong>Fair</strong> - Overwhelmed by 3+ cats\n                      </td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 p-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200\">\n                        1-2 days per application\n                      </td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 p-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200\">\n                        $15-20\n                      </td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 p-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200\">\n                        <strong>Scented Clay Additives</strong>\n                      </td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 p-3 text-red-700 dark:text-red-300\">\n                        <strong>Poor</strong> - Masks, doesn't eliminate\n                      </td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 p-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200\">\n                        2-3 days, then overpowering\n                      </td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 p-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200\">\n                        $30-45\n                      </td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 p-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200\">\n                        <strong>Enzymatic Sprays</strong>\n                      </td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 p-3 text-yellow-700 dark:text-yellow-300\">\n                        <strong>Good</strong> - For spot treatment only\n                      </td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 p-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200\">\n                        12-24 hours\n                      </td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 p-3 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200\">\n                        $40-60\n                      </td>\n                    </tr>\n                  </tbody>\n                </table>\n              </div>\n\n              <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mb-6\">Advanced Multi-Cat Strategies</h2>\n\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-6\">\n                Once you've mastered basic <strong>litter deodorizer for multiple cats</strong> application,\n                these advanced techniques will take your odor control to the professional level:\n              </p>\n\n              <div class=\"space-y-6 mb-8\">\n                <div class=\"bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-900/20 border border-purple-200 dark:border-purple-800 rounded-lg p-6\">\n                  <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-purple-900 dark:text-purple-100 mb-4\">üéØ Zone-Based Management</h3>\n                  <div class=\"space-y-3 text-purple-800 dark:text-purple-200\">\n                    <div>\n                      <strong>High-Traffic Zone:</strong> 2x daily deodorizer + premium activated carbon\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <strong>Medium-Traffic Zone:</strong> Daily maintenance + standard dosage\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <strong>Low-Traffic Zone:</strong> Every 2-3 days + light application\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <strong>Backup Boxes:</strong> Weekly refresh + preventive treatment\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"bg-teal-50 dark:bg-teal-900/20 border border-teal-200 dark:border-teal-800 rounded-lg p-6\">\n                  <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-teal-900 dark:text-teal-100 mb-4\">üìà Seasonal Adjustments</h3>\n                  <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-teal-800 dark:text-teal-200\">\n                    <div>\n                      <strong class=\"block mb-2\">üåû Summer (Higher Humidity)</strong>\n                      <ul class=\"space-y-1 text-sm\">\n                        <li>‚Ä¢ Increase deodorizer by 25%</li>\n                        <li>‚Ä¢ More frequent box changes</li>\n                        <li>‚Ä¢ Enhanced ventilation</li>\n                      </ul>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                      <strong class=\"block mb-2\">‚ùÑÔ∏è Winter (Closed Windows)</strong>\n                      <ul class=\"space-y-1 text-sm\">\n                        <li>‚Ä¢ Focus on air purifiers</li>\n                        <li>‚Ä¢ Standard deodorizer amounts</li>\n                        <li>‚Ä¢ Strategic fan placement</li>\n                      </ul>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-900/20 border border-orange-200 dark:border-orange-800 rounded-lg p-6\">\n                  <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-orange-900 dark:text-orange-100 mb-4\">üè† Whole-Home Integration</h3>\n                  <div class=\"space-y-3 text-orange-800 dark:text-orange-200\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start space-x-3\">\n                      <span>üí®</span>\n                      <div>\n                        <strong>HVAC Integration:</strong> Place activated carbon near air returns to treat circulated air\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start space-x-3\">\n                      <span>üßπ</span>\n                      <div>\n                        <strong>Floor Treatment:</strong> Light dusting of deodorizer around box areas prevents tracking odors\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start space-x-3\">\n                      <span>ü™£</span>\n                      <div>\n                        <strong>Waste Storage:</strong> Add carbon to waste containers for complete odor elimination\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <div class=\"mb-8\">\n                <img src=\"maintenanceImage\" alt=\"Cat owners troubleshooting and maintaining clean multi-cat litter areas\" />\n                <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-center mt-2\">\n                  Proper maintenance prevents common multi-cat odor issues\n                </p>\n              </div>\n\n              <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 mb-6\">Troubleshooting Multi-Cat Odor Problems</h2>\n\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-6\">\n                Even with the best <strong>multi-cat litter deodorizer</strong> products, challenges\n                can arise. Here are solutions to the most common multi-cat odor problems:\n              </p>\n\n              <div class=\"space-y-6 mb-8\">\n                <div class=\"border-l-4 border-red-500 dark:border-red-700 bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/20 p-6\">\n                  <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-red-900 dark:text-red-100 mb-3\">üî• Problem: Overwhelming Ammonia Smell</h3>\n                  <div class=\"text-red-800 dark:text-red-200 space-y-2\">\n                    <div><strong>Cause:</strong> Insufficient deodorizer or overdue box cleaning</div>\n                    <div><strong>Solution:</strong> Double deodorizer amount, increase cleaning frequency to twice daily</div>\n                    <div><strong>Prevention:</strong> Never skip the evening maintenance routine</div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"border-l-4 border-yellow-500 dark:border-yellow-700 bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900/20 p-6\">\n                  <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-yellow-900 dark:text-yellow-100 mb-3\">‚ö†Ô∏è Problem: One Box Smells Worse Than Others</h3>\n                  <div class=\"text-yellow-800 dark:text-yellow-200 space-y-2\">\n                    <div><strong>Cause:</strong> Territorial preference or medical issue with one cat</div>\n                    <div><strong>Solution:</strong> Triple deodorizer in problem box, check for underlying health issues</div>\n                    <div><strong>Prevention:</strong> Monitor individual cat bathroom habits</div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"border-l-4 border-blue-500 dark:border-blue-700 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 p-6\">\n                  <h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-blue-900 dark:text-blue-100 mb-3\">üíô Problem: Cats Avoiding Certain Boxes</h3>\n                  <div class=\"text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-200 space-y-2\">\n                    <div><strong>Cause:</strong> Over-deodorizing or using scented products</div>\n                    <div><strong>Solution:</strong> Reduce deodorizer by half, ensure fragrance-free formula</div>\n                    <div><strong>Prevention:</strong> Always use unscented, natural deodorizers like activated carbon</div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              <div class=\"bg-[#FF3131]/10 dark:bg-[#FF3131]/5 border border-[#FF3131]/20 dark:border-[#FF6B6B]/30 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8\">\n                <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[#FF3131] dark:text-[#FF6B6B] mb-